summary: Commissions!
title: Commissions!
body:
Hi there! Here is my commission pricing, along with examples!

Basic Screenshot edits are $10! Includes basic edits, minor repaints.

Complex screenshot edits are $15! Includes basic edits, more repainting, scenery change and clothing change!

Headshots are also $15! Includes simple background. I also do pet portraits!

Half bodies or busts are $20! Scenes start at $10, and extra characters are $10 each!

Full bodies or ¾ bodies are $25! Scenes start at $10 and extra characters are $15 each!
